title: 1977-03-11 Amsterdam
description:
Hawkwind, 11.03.1977, Amsterdam Paradiso   (11th March, 1977)

This is a 320 kbps mp3 version.  FLAC versions will be available elsewhere, I&#039;m sure.

Superb recording of a fantastic gig.  

There is a little bit of clipping during the intro and some tape hiss throughout, but it is not intrusive and does not detract from the excellence of this show.
